line_1: Quite through my Soul the charming Accents slide,
line_2: That from his Life inspiring Portals glide;

line_1: Round his clos'd sight the gorgeous curtain slide;
line_2: From goblets, high emboss'd, his wine must glide,

line_1: Back to my  native Moderation slide,
line_2: And win my way by yielding to the tyde.

line_1: Which wou'd still be apt to slide;
line_2: That a Staff, his Feet must guide,

line_1: Whose Waves, untouch't, through secret Channels slide,
line_2: Untainted, as the Silver Streams, that glide
